name: The World
description:
"To the world you may be but one, but to me you are my world"

2 Colour screen print.

From an original illustration of mine, then hand-printed, to just short of A3 size.

name: Get on your Bike
description:
"Get on your bike and think of nothing but the road in front of you"

2 colour screen print, from an original illustration of mine. The print area is just a smidge smaller than A3 - so fits in any standard size frame.

Available in two colours olive green and bright emerald green.  Small editions of this print: 15 printed in the olive and only 10 for the emerald - and when they are gone - they are GONE!

Both editions are currently on sale - normally £35- now £15 for the emerald and £25 for the olive green.
